data.description: Come check out this cutie in Lexington! This adorable home sits on a quiet, pleasant street right in the middle of town. This home naturally exudes curb appeal with fresh landscaping and the large front porch. Upon entering the home you will appreciate the large living area and spacious kitchen and dining spaces. The kitchen has all the cabinet and countertop space one could want or need. There are two bedrooms fitted with brand new carpet and a functional bathroom/laundry. The backyard offers a beautiful wood deck, perfect for relaxing and catching some sun. Additional features include a carport, fully fenced backyard, and storage space off the carport. Schedule your showing today!  ***This property qualifies for USDA 0% down financing!***
